title: Elements - Puzzle game
description:
First there was Tetris, then Bejeweled.... Now....
                        
                        " ELEMENTS "

A matching puzzler with a twist. Harness the power of nature's greatest forces in this addictive swap-and-match game. Over 50 levels, 15 unlockable elements, and three play modes, chart progress on the alchemists pentagram, wildcard gems make impossible matches. 

Very fun game, hope you enjoy it!

Just mount .iso in daemon tools or alchohol 120% install and play, no keys or exe's required.
